PRSS 2.0 is live. Get the AI powered Website Creator.

Build blogs, documentation sites, showcases and more with ease. Available for Windows, MacOS and Linux.

Version 1.16.0 is available!

  • Build: Perf improvements (minification not performed on preview build, only on deploy build). This cuts preview build time by half.
  • Variables Editor: A variable type can be changed by hovering over the icon.
  • Posts List: Dedicated buttons to create Page and create Post. Upon clicking "Create Post", the post will automatically have the "Blog" page as its parent.
  • Slug Editor: "Refresh Slug" button to recreate the slug according to the latest Post title.
  • Other minor UI adjustments.

Meet simplicity

Create your website effortlessly using a user-friendly interface. No need for registration, terminals or codes.

Local AI and GPT-3.5 Turbo Support

With support for self-hosted AI via Ollama, as well as GPT (with an OpenAI Key), you can say hello to autoblogging & rewriting features.

Local AI support means no more paying for blogging AI!

Full control at your fingertips

Choose from an ever-expanding selection of themes, edit them, or create your own. Built-in SEO, Sitemaps, Social media tags handling, and more.

Preview & Publish to Github Pages

With PRSS, you can preview your changes locally in your browser. When ready, you can publish to Github Pages or Self-host.

Real-world performance

Stop worrying about optimization and caching plugins. Your PRSS site is optimal out of the box. This is thanks to low dependencies, Content Delivery Network (CDN) and Server-side rendering (SSR) by default.
